Title: Agitated Screams of Maggots
Description: ['"Agitated Screams of Maggots" was directed by Keita Kurosaka and released in 2006 with the single, "Agitated Screams of Maggots", made by Japanese rock band, DIR EN GREY. ASOM has a traditional drawing design with erotic and grotesque aspects. The video had also received some attention from it\'s art style and was shown at the International Film Festival Rotterdam in 2007.']
